my best interest at heart.

39:05.637 --> 39:08.473
You know, Paul and I,
we just had some conversations. That's it.

39:11.310 --> 39:12.352
Yeah.

39:16.857 --> 39:18.442
You haven't told Cybil yet.

39:22.571 --> 39:24.406
