39:32.497 --> 39:34.291
you will be taken care of.

40:06.949 --> 40:08.659
God, I'm so sick of men.

40:09.868 --> 40:10.869
Thank you?

40:10.869 --> 40:15.541
- No, not you. Men with power.
- Again, thank you very much.

40:15.541 --> 40:16.792
That's nice.

40:17.668 --> 40:21.463
Paul fucking Marks.
Paul fucking Marks? Jesus.

40:21.463 --> 40:24.091
